7	finance/travel-expense-policy.md	Travel Expense Reimbursement	Travel expenses must be submitted within thirty days of trip completion. Receipts are required for lodging, airfare, rail travel, and any single expense over 25 dollars. Reimbursements are processed through payroll after manager approval and finance audit.	{"tags": ["travel", "expenses", "reimbursement"], "category": "policy", "department": "Finance", "chunk_index": 0, "access_groups": []}	[0.770914,0.919662,0.994286,0.981604,0.883857,0.718309,0.514201,0.307585,0.134956,0.026803,0.002232,0.065581,0.205661,0.39773,0.607863,0.798945,0.937223,0.998276,0.971318,0.861111,0.687122,0.480081,0.276558,0.112502,0.01689,0.006609,0.083475,0.233913,0.431349,0.64091,0.825583,0.952749,0.999945,0.958837,0.836684,0.655063,0.446053,0.246572,0.091854,0.009226,0.013284,0.10331,0.263403,0.465287,0.673301,0.850706,0.966165,0.999286,0.944218,0.810688,0.622282,0.412276,0.217766,0.073106,0.003848,0.022226,0.124992,0.293996,0.499386,0.704885,0.874195,0.977411,0.996302,0.927532,0.783246,0.588931,0.378908,0.190274,0.056346,0.000781,0.033392,0.148421,0.325548,0.533489,0.735515,0.895942,0.986434,0.991007,0.908854,0.754485,0.555167,0.346104,0.164224,0.041652,3.8e-05,0.046732,0.173486,0.357913,0.567436,0.765048,0.915844,0.993191,0.983425,0.888272,0.724539,0.521145,0.314017,0.139739,0.029093,0.001624,0.062183,0.200073,0.390939,0.601068,0.793346,0.933811,0.997651,0.973592,0.865882,0.693547,0.487025,0.282796,0.116931,0.018727,0.005531,0.079672,0.228056,0.424473,0.63423,0.820279,0.949757,0.999794,0.961553,0.841788,0.661653,0.452966,0.252586,0.095907,0.010602,0.01174,0.099119,0.257305,0.458359,0.666767,0.84572,0.963608,0.999609,0.947365,0.816102,0.629007,0.419125,0.223528,0.076764,0.004757,0.020223,0.120433,0.287685,0.492438,0.698527,0.869551,0.9753,0.997098,0.931093,0.788945,0.59576,0.385661,0.195758,0.059593,0.001217,0.030941,0.143514,0.319054,0.526553,0.729363,0.891661,0.984779,0.992271,0.912814,0.760441,0.562067,0.35273,0.169405,0.0444